(18, 17, 1, 1, 'bledixhindi', 'Ankete per sektet fetare', '<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">1. A besoni ne nje sekt fetar?</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Po/Jo</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/>2. A keni shkuar ndonje here ne mbledhje rreth ketij sekti?</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Po/Jo</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/>3. A keni perfituar ndonje here para nga ky lloje sekti?</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Po/Jo</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/>4. A ju ka detyruar ky lloje sekti te beni veprime qe ju nuk i deshironi?</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Po/Jo</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/>5. Ne sektin fetar ku ju beni pjese a eshte fjala e lire?</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Po/Jo</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/>6. Sa besoni ne kete sekt fetar.<br/> Pak/Shume</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/>7. A ka ky sekt fetar festa qe ju i festoni?Dhe cilat jan ato? </p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">Po/Jo</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><br/>.............................................................................................................