(20, 19, 1, 1, 'bledixhindi', 'Ankete mbi besimin fetar', '<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>ANKETE MBI BESIMIN FETAR</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong> </strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>1-Pershendetje! A besoni ne nje sekt fetar? Nese po, ne cilin sekt?</strong></p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Po</p></li><li><p>Jo</p></li></ul><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>………………………………………………………………………………………………………</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>2- Deri ne cilin nivel e konsideroni veten besimtare?</strong></p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Jo besimtare</p></li><li><p>Pak besimtare</p></li><li><p>Besimtare normal</p></li><li><p>Shume besimtare</p></li><li><p>Nuk e di</p></li></ul><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>3- Sipas mendimit tuaj, a ka ndryshime midis te qenurit besimtare dhe spiritual?</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>4- A i frekuentoni vendet e praktikimit te besimit tuaj?</strong></p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Po</p></li><li><p>Jo</p></li></ul><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>5- Cilat jane disa nga festat fetare qe ju festoni?</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>6- A keni lexuar ndonje shkrim te shenjte fetar te besimit tuaj dhe nese po, cfare mbresash ju ka lene?</strong></p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Po</p></li><li><p>Jo</p></li></ul><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………………</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>7- Sa shpesh mendon se besimi juaj ju ndihmon ne veprimtarite tuaja te perditshme?</strong></p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Asnjehere</p></li><li><p>Ndonjehere</p></li><li><p>Shpeshhere</p></li><li><p>Gjithmone</p></li></ul><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong> </strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong> </strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>8- Sipas mendimit tuaj, si do ta pershkruanit Zotin?</strong></p><ul style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>Gjithmone i pranishem</p></li><li><p>Ndeshkues</p></li><li><p>Kritikues</p></li><li><p>I distancuar</p></li><li><p>Tolerant</p></li><li><p>Tjeter<strong>(……………………………………………………………………………….)</strong></p></li></ul><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\"><strong>9- Faleminderit per kohen e kushtuar!</strong></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">a)      Faleminderit dhe ju!</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">b)      Shyqyr qe mbaruam!</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: medium; white-space: normal;\">c)      OK.</p><p><br/></p>', '185.89.159.80', 1633555047, 0),
